{
  "scenes": [
    {
      "id": "village_forest_entrance",
      "name": "Village - Entrance",
      "paragraphs": [
        "You enter the village. It looks quite nice and is of a moderate size!",
        "You look back and the door is already shut closed.",
        "The village square is just before you."
      ],
      "actions": [
        {
          "text": "Go to Village Square",
          "triggers": [
            {
              "type": "movement",
              "target": "village_square"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "village_square",
      "name": "Village - Square",
      "paragraphs": [
        "The square is connected to most areas in the village."
      ],
      "actions": [
        {
          "text": "Go to Tavern",
          "triggers": [
            {
              "type": "movement",
              "target": "village_tavern"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "Go to Quest Board",
          "triggers": [
            {
              "type": "movement",
              "target": "village_square_quest_board"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "Go to the Village Shop",
          "triggers": [
            {
              "type": "movement",
              "target": "village_shop_1"
            }
          ],
          "showAny": [
            "opened_village_shop"
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "Go to the Village Docks",
          "triggers": [
            {
              "type": "movement",
              "target": "village_dock_1"
            }
          ],
          "showAny": [
            "village_dock_opened"
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "Go to Orchards by the High Roads",
          "showAny": [
            "opened_village_orchard"
          ],
          "triggers": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "village_square_quest_board",
      "name": "Village - Square - Quest Board",
      "paragraphs": [
        "Here you see all the available quests in the village.",
        {
          "text": "For the moment only unemployment seems available.",
          "hideAny": [
            "opened_village_quest_board_backside"
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "The description from the barkeep seems true -- There seems to be something on the backside of the quest board.",
          "showAny": [
            "opened_village_quest_board_backside"
          ]
        }
      ],
      "actions": [
        {
          "text": "Inspect backside",
          "triggers": [
            {
              "type": "movement",
              "target": "village_square_quest_board_backside"
            }
          ],
          "showAny": [
            "opened_village_quest_board_backside"
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "Step back",
          "triggers": [
            {
              "type": "movement",
              "target": "village_square"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "village_tavern",
      "name": "Village - Tavern",
      "paragraphs": [
        "The first thing that strikes you is the noise. Fishermen know how to keep it lively.",
        "The tavern smells of good food and drinks - thankfully not too fishy.",
        {
          "text": "> You ask the barkeep about any quests. He recommend checking out the backside of the quest board for the... unusual quests.",
          "showAny": [
            "opened_village_quest_board_backside"
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "> You ask the barkeep about shops for perusing any goods. He tips you about the village shop not far from the village square.",
          "showAny": [
            "opened_village_shop"
          ]
        }
      ],
      "actions": [
        {
          "text": "Ask barkeep about quests",
          "triggers": [
            {
              "type": "add_flag",
              "target": "opened_village_quest_board_backside"
            }
          ],
          "hideAny": [
            "opened_village_quest_board_backside"
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "Ask barkeep about shops",
          "triggers": [
            {
              "type": "add_flag",
              "target": "opened_village_shop"
            }
          ],
          "hideAny": [
            "opened_village_shop"
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "Back to Village Square",
          "triggers": [
            {
              "type": "movement",
              "target": "village_square"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "village_square_quest_board_backside",
      "name": "Quest Board - Backside",
      "paragraphs": [
        "The backside of the quest board. ",
        "A note hangs there.",
        {
          "text": "> You touch the backside. It is greasy and slimy. Ew, why did you do that? Now your fingers smells like week old fish.",
          "showAny": [
            "village_square_quest_board_backside_touched_it"
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "> You transferred most of the greasiness and sliminess onto the note. Even the village cat would find the fishy smell revolting.",
          "showAny": [
            "village_square_quest_board_backside_wiped_fingers"
          ]
        }
      ],
      "actions": [
        {
          "text": "Touch the backside",
          "triggers": [
            {
              "type": "add_flag",
              "target": "village_square_quest_board_backside_touched_it"
            }
          ],
          "hideAny": [
            "village_square_quest_board_backside_touched_it"
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "Wipe your fingers on the note",
          "triggers": [
            {
              "type": "add_flag",
              "target": "village_square_quest_board_backside_wiped_fingers"
            }
          ],
          "showAny": [
            "village_square_quest_board_backside_touched_it"
          ],
          "hideAny": [
            "village_square_quest_board_backside_wiped_fingers"
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "Inspect the note",
          "triggers": [
            {
              "type": "add_flag",
              "target": "quest_board_backside_quest_inspected_note"
            },
            {
              "type": "movement",
              "target": "quest_board_backside_quest"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "Go back",
          "triggers": [
            {
              "type": "movement",
              "target": "village_square_quest_board"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "quest_board_backside_quest",
      "name": "Quest Board - Backside - Note",
      "paragraphs": [
        "\"Talk to me for some extra coins.\"\n",
        "\"Oh by the way, very legal. Yes very.\"",
        "\"By the way by the way, this is the shop keeper.\""
      ],
      "actions": [
        {
          "text": "Go back",
          "triggers": [
            {
              "type": "movement",
              "target": "village_square_quest_board_backside"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "village_shop_1",
      "name": "Village - Shop",
      "paragraphs": [
        "\"How are ya?\", the shopkeeper says. \"Looking a bit... wet.\"",
        "\"Anyway, look at my wares!\" He points at an assortment of different goods.",
        {
          "text": "> You look at the wares. There isn't anything worth anything here. Maybe try your luck at a later time?",
          "showAny": [
            "village_shopkeeper_looked_at_wares"
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "This man gave you a quest. A quest you have yet to complete.",
          "showAny": [
            "village_shop_took_quest"
          ],
          "hideAny": [
            "village_shop_completed_quest"
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "This man gave you a quest. A quest you have completed.",
          "showAll": [
            "village_shop_took_quest",
            "village_shop_completed_quest"
          ]
        }
      ],
      "actions": [
        {
          "text": "Take a look",
          "triggers": [
            {
              "type": "add_flag",
              "target": "village_shopkeeper_looked_at_wares"
            }
          ],
          "hideAny": [
            "village_shopkeeper_looked_at_wares"
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "Ask about the note",
          "triggers": [
            {
              "type": "movement",
              "target": "village_shop_2"
            }
          ],
          "showAny": [
            "quest_board_backside_quest_inspected_note"
          ],
          "hideAny": [
            "village_shop_took_quest"
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "Go back",
          "triggers": [
            {
              "type": "movement",
              "target": "village_square",
              "chapterId": "chapter_4"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "village_shop_2",
      "name": "Village - Shop - Secret Quest",
      "paragraphs": [
        "\"Oooh, askin' about the secret quest, are ya? Well, ya seem like a decent fellow. Let's see if ya're up'n'to the task.\"",
        "The shopkeeper reaches down. A small package is presents itself to you on the vendors table.",
        "\"Ya agree to the job?\"",
        {
          "text": "> You try to take the package.",
          "showAny": [
            "village_shop_took_package_too_early"
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "\"Ya daft head! Agree to the job before taking the package. These young'ins...\"",
          "showAny": [
            "village_shop_took_package_too_early"
          ]
        }
      ],
      "actions": [
        {
          "text": "Take package",
          "triggers": [
            {
              "type": "add_flag",
              "target": "village_shop_took_package_too_early"
            }
          ],
          "hideAny": [
            "village_shop_took_package",
            "village_shop_took_quest",
            "village_shop_took_package_too_early"
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "Agree to the job",
          "triggers": [
            {
              "type": "add_flag",
              "target": "village_shop_took_quest"
            },
            {
              "type": "movement",
              "target": "village_shop_3"
            }
          ],
          "hideAny": [
            "village_shop_took_quest"
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "Take package",
          "triggers": [
            {
              "type": "add_flag",
              "target": "village_shop_took_package"
            },
            {
              "type": "add_flag",
              "target": "village_dock_opened"
            }
          ],
          "hideAny": [
            "village_shop_took_package"
          ],
          "showAny": [
            "village_shop_took_quest"
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "Go back",
          "triggers": [
            {
              "type": "movement",
              "target": "village_square",
              "chapterId": "chapter_4"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "village_dock_1",
      "name": "Village - Dock",
      "paragraphs": [
        "The grand docks of the Village. It fits two ships. Two very small fishing ships. Like row boat small."
      ],
      "actions": [
        {
          "text": "Go to Village Square",
          "triggers": [
            {
              "type": "movement",
              "target": "village_square"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "village_shop_3",
      "name": "Village - Shop - Secret Quest",
      "paragraphs": [
        {
          "text": "You reluctantly agree to the job. ",
          "showAll": [
            "village_shop_took_package_too_early"
          ],
          "ignoreSortByFlag": true
        },
        {
          "text": "The shop keeper looks suspiciously at you.",
          "showAll": [
            "village_shop_took_package_too_early"
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "You nod to the shop keeper, taking the secret quest.\n",
          "hideAny": [
            "village_shop_took_package_too_early"
          ],
          "ignoreSortByFlag": true
        },
        {
          "text": "\"Good lad.\"",
          "hideAny": [
            "village_shop_took_package_too_early"
          ],
          "ignoreSortByFlag": true
        },
        {
          "text": "\"Take this one to the dock master.\" He looks you in the eye. \"Remember this! This is very important. Tell him this is from Albert the 4th of the Vicount's 9th son! Veeery important you remember that.\"",
          "ignoreSortByFlag": true
        },
        {
          "text": "> You take the package.",
          "showAny": [
            "village_shop_took_package"
          ],
          "ignoreSortByFlag": true
        },
        {
          "text": "He pats your back. \"Now get!\"",
          "showAny": [
            "village_shop_took_package"
          ],
          "ignoreSortByFlag": true
        }
      ],
      "actions": [
        {
          "text": "Take package",
          "triggers": [
            {
              "type": "add_flag",
              "target": "village_shop_took_package"
            },
            {
              "type": "add_flag",
              "target": "village_dock_opened"
            }
          ],
          "hideAny": [
            "village_shop_took_package"
          ],
          "showAny": [
            "village_shop_took_quest"
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "Go back",
          "triggers": [
            {
              "type": "movement",
              "target": "village_square",
              "chapterId": "chapter_4"
            }
          ],
          "showAny": [
            "village_shop_took_package"
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
